OL,3,CDangerous drugs stored incorrectly at
OL,4,Ccare home where man died, a court hears
OL,6,FThe drugs mistakenly given to a man
OL,7,Fwho later died were incorrectly stored
OL,8,Fat the care home in which he lived, a
OL,9,Fcourt has heard.
OL,11,FJane Barnard, 67, denies the
OL,12,Fmanslaughter of 75-year-old Derek
OL,13,FDavies, who lived at the care home
OL,14,Fwhere she was employed.
OL,16,FMr Davies died on September 8, 2021,
OL,17,Fafter Barnard mistakenly gave him
OL,18,Fmedication prescribed for another
OL,19,Fpatient, Jason Dodsworth, including
OL,20,F90mg of slow-release morphine.
