OL,6,FA trial at Gloucester Crown Court
OL,7,Fheard the morphine, a controlled drug,
OL,8,Fhad been stored in the wrong place
OL,9,Fwhen it was retrieved by Barnard.
OL,11,FThe controlled drugs at Wheatridge
OL,12,FCourt care home were meant to be
OL,13,Flocked away in a designated room and
OL,14,Fonly administered with two members of
OL,15,Fstaff present, the court was told.
