OL,3,CDangerous drugs stored incorrectly at
OL,4,Ccare home where man died, a court hears
OL,6,FHowever, Mr Dodsworth's morphine had
OL,7,Fbeen incorrectly stored in his
OL,8,Fbathroom cabinet. While Barnard was
OL,9,Fnot involved in storing the
OL,10,Fmedication, the court heard she had
OL,11,Ffailed to make the correct checks and
OL,12,Ffollow procedure before administering
OL,13,Fthe controlled drug.
OL,15,FCrucially, she also took the drugs to
OL,16,Fthe wrong resident, Mr Davies, who had
OL,17,Fbeen sitting in a communal area of the
OL,18,Fhome.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
