OL,3,CDangerous drugs stored incorrectly at
OL,4,Ccare home where man died, a court hears
OL,6,FAndrew Langdon KC, defending, said:
OL,7,F"These controlled drugs were not, in
OL,8,Ffact, being properly controlled.
OL,10,F"There had been no proper risk
OL,11,Fassessment of Jason Dodsworth's drugs,
OL,12,Ftwo others had failed to spot the
OL,13,Fmorphine when booking the drugs in.
OL,15,F"We do not blame them for what went
OL,16,Fwrong, everyone was under pressure,
OL,17,Fthese are hard-working people who are
OL,18,Fnot paid much and they do their very
OL,19,Fbest.
