OL,6,F"It seems that standards, usually high
OL,7,Fin the home no doubt, had slipped. But
OL,8,Fit is not the manager or the home on
OL,9,Ftrial, it is Jane Barnard."
OL,11,FBarnard, of Longlevens, Gloucester,
OL,12,Fwas employed as a care worker at
OL,13,FWheatridge Court in Abbeydale,
OL,14,FGloucester, where Mr Davies was a
OL,15,Fresident when he died.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]
