OL,3,CDangerous drugs stored incorrectly at
OL,4,Ccare home where man died, a court hears
OL,6,FBarnard said she was in a "state" and
OL,7,Fcould not bring herself to tell
OL,8,Fcolleagues or medical professionals
OL,9,Fwhat she had done, even after Mr
OL,10,FDavies fell ill and was taken to
OL,11,Fhospital.
OL,13,FOn September 8, two days after the
OL,14,Fincident, Barnard rang Kim Jones,
OL,15,Fdeputy manager of the home, to tell
OL,16,Fher she had given Mr Davies the wrong
OL,17,Fmedication.
OL,26,@nD@[OUnD@aO]
