OL,6,FWhen the care home contacted the
OL,7,Fhospital, it was confirmed Mr Davies
OL,8,Fhad died that morning. Mr Langdon
OL,9,Fsuggested Barnard might have expected
OL,10,FMr Davies to fall ill, but could not
OL,11,Fhave foreseen his death.
OL,13,FThe original cause of death was
OL,14,Fdocumented as a brainstem stroke, but
OL,15,Fit was later understood the actual
OL,16,Fcause of Mr Davies' death was a
OL,17,Fconsequence of morphine toxicity.
OL,19,FAt the time of the incident Barnard
OL,20,Fhad been employed as a care worker at
OL,21,FWheatridge Court for 32 years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
