OL,6,F"Until that moment, she had led a life
OL,7,Fthat would make any of us proud," Mr
OL,8,FLangdon added. "She made a terrible
OL,9,Fmistake."
OL,11,FThe jury has retired to consider its
OL,12,Fverdict.
